item.title: How to change max stats to 99 & cmb to 126
item.dc:creator: @Slivion Slivion
item.description:
@Slivion wrote:

Find out the max experiene that you would like. Then open up your client. Hold ctrl and f. Search for.

995000

It should be longer than that when you find it. Change it to the experience you would like. You can change it to the experience on level 99.

If you don’t have that number search the max experience on your server.
